  "comment": "Stage Blinder 100 Blaze is a powerful 100-watt LED blinder that uses a warm white COB LED of 3000 K with a CRI of >92. It has uniquely integrated amber LEDs for mimicking a tungsten dim effect and RGB LEDs for a blaze effect. It can be controlled via DMX/RDM, but also has manual, master/slave and auto modes. The OLED display provides useful feedback on the settings.\n\nIt has silent convection cooling, making it suitable for noise-sensitive environments. The robust aluminum housing is IP65-rated and comes with a mounting bracket.",
